'''奥尔巴尼法学院'''（Albany Law School）是一所自1851年起在[[美国|美国]][[纽约州|纽约州]][[奥尔巴尼|奥尔巴尼]]创设的法学院，形式上附属于[[联合大学|联合大学]]（{{link-en|Union University (New York)}}），实际上不附属于任何大学。

==历史==
2010年开始，该院的学生就在不断减少<ref name="Albany Profs Deny Faculty Suggested Cutting">{{cite news|last=Caher|first=John|title=Albany Profs Deny Faculty Suggested Cutting Standards|url=http://www.newyorklawjournal.com/id=1202641880915/Albany+Profs+Deny+Faculty+Suggested+Cutting+Standards%3Fmcode=0&curindex=0&curpage=ALL|accessdate=7 February 2014|newspaper=The New York Law Journal|date=February 6, 2014}}{{Dead link}}</ref>，为了维持正常运转学院开始裁员<ref>{{cite news|last=Caher|first=John|title=Albany Law Offers Buyouts to Offset Lower Enrollment|url=http://www.newyorklawjournal.com/home/id=1202641330977/Albany+Law+Offers+Buyouts+to+Offset+Lower+Enrollment%3Fmcode=1202614952687&curindex=2#|accessdate=7 February 2014|newspaper=The New York Law Journal|date=February 4, 2014|archive-date=2017-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170111121400/http://www.newyorklawjournal.com/home/id%3D1202641330977/Albany+Law+Offers+Buyouts+to+Offset+Lower+Enrollment%3Fmcode%3D1202614952687%26curindex%3D2|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，很多教授对裁员不满，集体向[[美国律师协会|美国律师协会]]投诉。<ref name="Albany Profs Deny Faculty Suggested Cutting" />

==排名==
该学院在《[[2020美国新闻与世界报道|2020美国新闻与世界报道]]》的[[美国法学院排名|法学院排名]]中排第115名。<ref name="Top 2020 Law School Rankings">{{cite web | url=https://www.usnews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/albany-law-school-03101 | title=Top 2020 Law School Rankings | accessdate=2019-12-24 | archive-date=2021-02-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202141629/https://www.usnews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/albany-law-school-03101 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==校友==
该校校友包括两名[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]的法官，[[罗伯特·H·杰克逊|罗伯特·H·杰克逊]]和[[David_Josiah_Brewer|David Josiah Brewer]]，7名[[纽约上诉法院|纽约上诉法院]]的法官，美国总统，纽约州州长[[安德鲁·库默|安德鲁·库默]]等人。

